Cleric of Mitra Guild Levels

Clerics rise through righteous battle. Every worthy kill earns Cleric
XP, and your guild level rises automatically when you have earned
enough. Type 'cost' or 'advance guild' at the guild hall to see your
progress.

Level	Title			Cleric XP to reach
=====   ===============		==================
  1	Aspiring Acolyte	       0
  2	Acolyte			    1000
  3	Adept			    2000
  4	Evangelist		    3000
  5	Ecclesiastic		    5000
  6	Curate			    7000
  7	Predicant		   10000
  8	Canon			   13000
  9	Minister		   16000
 10	Patriarch		   20000
 11	Spiritual One		   24000
 12	Blessed One		   28000
 13	Divine One		   32000
 14	Chosen One		   36000
 15	Saviour			   40000

Your guild level can never exceed your character level, and your
combined guild levels can never exceed your character level. Mitra
grants nothing while your alignment is evil - XP earned while you
stray is banked, and the levels pop when you atone. At guild level
15 her Champions join the himitra and saviour channels.

Your battle record survives leaving the guild. Should you return in
good standing, your guild level is restored.
